*Sumnjam* da će se stvari promeniti. (I doubt that things will change.)

*Sumnjala* sam da ću uspeti da završim zadatak. (I doubted that I would be able to finish the task.)

*Sumnjalo* se da će projekat biti uspešan. (It was doubted that the project will be successful.)

*Sumnjao* sam da je njegova priča tačna. (I doubted that his story was true.)

*Sumnjali* smo da će biti problema sa našim planom. (We doubted that there will be problems with our plan.)